{{Italic title}} {{Taxobox | image_caption = | name = ''Flexilinea'' | regnum = [[Bacterium|Bacteria]] | phylum = [[Chloroflexi (phylum)|Chloroflexi]] | classis = [[Anaerolineae]] | ordo = [[Anaerolineales]] | familia = [[Anaerolineaceae]] | genus = '''''Flexilinea''''' | genus_authority = Sun et al. 2016<ref name=Flexilinea>{{cite journal|last1=Parte|first1=A.C.|title=Flexilinea|journal=Www.bacterio.net|url=http://www.bacterio.net/flexilinea.html}}</ref> | type_species = ''Flexilinea flocculi''<ref name=Flexilinea/> |subdivision_ranks = [[Species]] |subdivision =''[[Flexilinea flocculi|F. flocculi]]''<ref name=Flexilinea/> }}
'''''Flexilinea''''' is a bacteria genus from the family of [[Anaerolineaceae]] with one known species (''[[Flexilinea flocculi]]'').<ref name=Flexilinea/><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Parker|first1=Charles Thomas|last2=Garrity|first2=George M|title=Nomenclature Abstract for Flexilinea Sun et al. 2016|journal=The NamesforLife Abstracts|doi=10.1601/nm.28432|language=en|year=2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Flexilinea|journal=Www.uniprot.org|url=https://www.uniprot.org/taxonomy/1769713|language=en}}</ref><ref name=PMID>{{cite journal|last1=Sun|first1=L|last2=Toyonaga|first2=M|last3=Ohashi|first3=A|last4=Matsuura|first4=N|last5=Tourlousse|first5=DM|last6=Meng|first6=XY|last7=Tamaki|first7=H|last8=Hanada|first8=S|last9=Cruz|first9=R|last10=Yamaguchi|first10=T|last11=Sekiguchi|first11=Y|title=Isolation and characterization of ''Flexilinea flocculi'' gen. nov., sp. nov., a filamentous, anaerobic bacterium belonging to the class ''Anaerolineae'' in the phylum ''Chloroflexi''.|journal=International Journal of Systematic and Evolutionary Microbiology|date=February 2016|volume=66|issue=2|pages=988–996|doi=10.1099/ijsem.0.000822|pmid=26637817}}</ref> ''Flexilinea flocculi'' has been isolated from methanogenic granular sludge.<ref name=PMID/>
